NET Stylesheets README
—by Brendon, {{ "2021/03/11" | date: dateFormat }}.

——Dependencies
`base.css` is required for all others. In addition, `form.css` uses the
`--lineHeight` variable from `document.css`, and can be made independent of it
by defining `--lineHeight` in `form.css/body`.

——Unagi
`form.css` and `input.css` are parts of Unagi.
